#ROOMS
#16450
Hall of Broken Mirrors.~
Shattered dreams lay to rest here, as you appear
within a bizzarre, gothic hallway. Upon the walls are
very dim torches, and broken mirrors laying between
them.  A long violet satin carpet extends to a very
ornate, yet slightly tarnished throne. Sitting atop it
is a raven statue, and it watches you very curiously,
its onyx eyes shimmering and gleaming. 
If you walk up the stairs you will find yourself in
Midgaard, or down towards the Great Spirit of Malkav
himself.
~
