#16451
The Path of Madness.~
In the center of this room, a large pentagram
rests, a dark figure standing in its midst, babbling
mindlessly. As the rest of this dark tower, there are
no windows, barely any doors. Just your own eyesight
and instincts to guide you. This entire realm seems to
reflect Ishamael's own heart and soul, if he were to
hold these anymore. The hall has a very romantic and
tragic feel and look, long violet draparies, and
paintings of Ishamael's long dead family, the
Forsaken. They all seem cadaverous as Ishamael, but a
bit older and more deadly seeming. If you walk further
down the hall you see the paintings in more detail, as
they lead into other portions of the realm.
~
