#16452
The Forsaken Paintings.~
A simple end to the Path of Shadows, you see the
paintings of the Forsaken surrounding you. You feel
that these are not just ordinary paintings, but
portals into the unknown. A pedestal lies in the midst
of this room, a dark forboding mist surrounding it.
Looking in it you see the destinations that lie ahead,
If you but focus upon them, and speak the names.
     The Book of Nod rests atop a large black marble pedestal, within it containing vast tomes of Kindred
knowledge..
~
